			<body><div id="52--the-apparition">

				<pb facs="/images/battle-pieces-v1/battle-pieces-i-0163.jpg"/>
				<head type="main">
				<hi rend="italic">The Apparition.</hi>
				</head>
				<head type="sub-head">
				<hi rend="italic">(A Retrospect.)</hi>
				</head>
<lg>
<l><hi rend="smallcaps">Convulsions</hi> came; and, where the field</l>
<l rend="2em">Long slept in pastoral green,</l>
<l>A goblin-mountain was upheaved</l>
<l>(Sure the scared sense was all deceived),</l>
<l n="5" rend="2em">Marl-glen and slag-ravine.</l>
</lg>
<lg>
<l>The unreserve of Ill was there,</l>
<l rend="2em">The clinkers in her last retreat;</l>
<l>But, ere the eye could take it in,</l>
<l>Or mind could comprehension win,</l>
<l n="10" rend="2em">It sunk!—and at our feet.</l>
</lg>
<lg>
<l>So, then, Solidity&apos;s a crust—</l>
<l rend="2em">The core of fire below;</l>
<l>All may go well for many a year,</l>
<l>But who can think without a fear</l>
<l n="15" rend="2em">Of horrors that happen so?</l>
</lg>

</div></body>
